  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PinDrop: Escape The Room is a single-player horror adventure that thrusts you into a dark, procedurally generated world where zombies hunt by sound. Survival depends on absolute silence, making stealth your only weapon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The question isn’t just if you’ll survive, but how long you can play before the undead catch up. Among the four exits, one of the four doors is the true door, your only path to freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/5dd153f29a9bdc423824c7a4c382a29c.poster.avif?t=1737908717\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/5dd153f29a9bdc423824c7a4c382a29c.webm?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/5dd153f29a9bdc423824c7a4c382a29c.mp4?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relentless Tension</strong> – Enter an immersive nightmare world where every sound could be your last. Hide, move carefully, and stay silent to avoid terrifying encounters with the undead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/65df59a8c49fcab3507d37a70e126c9e.poster.avif?t=1737908717\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/65df59a8c49fcab3507d37a70e126c9e.webm?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/65df59a8c49fcab3507d37a70e126c9e.mp4?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unpredictable World</strong> – Explore a landscape that constantly shifts with random object spawns and nonlinear paths, ensuring no two playthroughs are ever the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/ff79b4b9425365f2b0cac0aa59852f16.poster.avif?t=1737908717\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/ff79b4b9425365f2b0cac0aa59852f16.webm?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/ff79b4b9425365f2b0cac0aa59852f16.mp4?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Light Mechanics</strong> – Your torch can guide or betray you. Scavenge batteries, use light carefully, and balance survival with silence to outwit your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a brutal, sound sensitive journey that will test your nerves. How long can you play before silence fails you?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PinDrop: Escape The Room is a single-player horror adventure that thrusts you into a dark, procedurally generated world where zombies hunt by sound. Survival depends on absolute silence, making stealth your only weapon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The question isn’t just if you’ll survive, but how long you can play before the undead catch up. Among the four exits, one of the four doors is the true door, your only path to freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/5dd153f29a9bdc423824c7a4c382a29c.poster.avif?t=1737908717\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/5dd153f29a9bdc423824c7a4c382a29c.webm?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/5dd153f29a9bdc423824c7a4c382a29c.mp4?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relentless Tension</strong> – Enter an immersive nightmare world where every sound could be your last. Hide, move carefully, and stay silent to avoid terrifying encounters with the undead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/65df59a8c49fcab3507d37a70e126c9e.poster.avif?t=1737908717\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/65df59a8c49fcab3507d37a70e126c9e.webm?t=1737908717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic